{"tid":380451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【為超自然台開路】香港邊間廟最靈?","createTime":"2017-08-30T06:29:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T10:52:52.000Z","uid":97415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99ca4f9509da4bb4dc74200cc1cad658ecd05390","tid":380451,"uid":97415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:29:45.000Z","msg":"去日本買御守買得多，人地都係三百幾YEN一個。<br />\n<br />\n點解唔去香港搵陀地廟拜下問下？<br />\n<br />\n聽人講旺角山東街間水宮好撚準，廟街果三間廟好撚陰。<br />\n<br />\n之前撞去兩間燒野，廟制果間個廟祝直情叫我走，<br />\n<br />\n大家有冇差唔多經驗？<br />\n<br />\n利申：去灣仔姻緣石拜完之後半個月追到而家女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46d99da38934ba7d8a097c42f39be43581ec1c1","tid":380451,"uid":97415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:45:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306d7b865e71e138a9326a5d013ae5924437a8a8","tid":380451,"uid":96965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:56:40.000Z","msg":"屯門醫院"},{"pid":"e6cc65889114f99f17eae42da2c26ead67ecbf6e","tid":380451,"uid":97415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T06:58:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屯門醫院</blockquote><br />\n屯門醫院有廟咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715e00dfce4a4490a3e20657cd785e92adce1a69","tid":380451,"uid":97415,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T07:45:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff8b66774768ff96a1f8668860a900c10481402","tid":380451,"uid":62603,"like":